      "fog-of-war",
      "game",
      "generator",
      "libtcod",
      "map",
      "pathfinding",
      "random",
      "roguelike"
    ],
    "license": "MIT"
  },
  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "RogueSharp is a free library written in C# to help [roguelike](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roguelike \"roguelike\") developers get a head start on their game. RogueSharp provides many utility functions for dealing with map generation, field-of-view calculations, path finding, random number generation and more.",
    "context": "RogueSharp is a free library written in C# to help [roguelike](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roguelike \"roguelike\") developers get a head start on their game. RogueSharp provides many utility functions for dealing with map generation, field-of-view calculations, path finding, random number generation and more.\n\nIt is loosely based on the popular [libtcod](http://doryen.eptalys.net/libtcod/ \"libtcod\") or \"Doryen Library\" though not all features overlap.",
    "cynefinDomain": "complex"
  },
